name: power of three bangles
description:
Three bracelets are intertwined each different from the last. One of the bracelets is made from fine silver and has a delicate concave curve. The remaining two are made from sterling wire and have been distressed in different ways. 

These bracelets measure about 2 1/2" across and will make a pleasing sound on your wrist.

They also look great with my skinny gemstone bangles.

*Each set is handmade and will vary slightly from this photo.

name: rose window
description: Maple wood cutouts remind me of the brilliant rose windows and stunning architecture found in European cathedrals.  These large geometric circles are paired with rich rubies and bright sterling silver.  These earrings are  1 1/2" in diameter and will gently sway 2 1/2" from your earlobe.  Fun and lightweight.

name: skinny bangle amethyst
description:
A whole bunch of beautiful faceted dark amethyst stones sparkle from within the folds of this fine silver bracelet. The stones are held securely in place by sterling wire. The bracelet was hand formed and then hammered so it's pretty from all angles. 

The bangle is 1/4" thick, a little over 2 1/2" diameter and looks great with my power of three bangle bracelets or other gemstone skinnys (sold separately).

name: golden lasso
description: Simple and delicate lassos loop around to form a tear drop shape on your ear. The bottoms of the earrings have been lightly hammered to catch the light and add to their rustic charm. These earrings were hand formed from sturdy 18 gauge gold filled wire. They are about 1" across and will hand 1 1/2" from your earlobe,

name: lantern pendant
description:
A beautiful faceted green amethyst hangs like a beacon from layers of *argentium silver. The metal has been oxidized and then brushed away in all the right spots to bring out the layered details. The pendant dangles from a sterling ring that has been lightly hammered to catch the light. This pendant is on an 16" sterling chain with an easy lobster clasp. Pendant is 1 1/2" long and about 1/2" wide.

*argentium is silver that has been specially formulated to resist tarnish.
